ning.  %0a%3c %0a%3c Interestingly, although there is relation, these are not the same channels. Hand slips do not occur at the same time as mouth ones do, when in parallel. Instead, these happen independently of each other, even though there is large similarity in the mental processes that led to the slip. %0a%3c %0a%3c Sources: %0a%3c https://theconversation.com/why-do-people-have-slips-of-the-tongue-191383%0a%3c https://sites.google.com/a/students.colgate.edu/insights-from-sign-language/home/production-errors%0a%3c https://twitter.com/jahochcam/status/1592645656120012802%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Expansions:%0a%3c [[#expansions]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#expansionsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%3c %0a%3c (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:elseif [ equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:andrewid} '' || equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:section} '' ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c You must enter your andrew ID and section before submitting an expansion. %0a%3c %0a%3c (:else:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Comments%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:if equal {$Author} {$:Author}:)%0a%3c !!Change article category%0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#changearticlecategory:)%0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c (:Section: E:)%0a%3c (:Category: SignLanguage:)%0a%3c (:Title: Sign language slips:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
